{"tid":1000362,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[DSE 物理 2018] 問書/技巧分享","createTime":"2019-01-29T11:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T13:51:05.000Z","uid":171256,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7ce70e61a34f21df8b41bb410687f99805320b87","tid":1000362,"uid":171256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:14:19.000Z","msg":"上年，都開過類似嘅post，答下大家問題<br />\n<br />\n講下自己<br />\n物理系，隔左幾年讀書，工作，今年讀Phy PGDE，如無意外，下年會入中學教書。<br />\n上年，前年，私補嘅學生全部都5**，(都有狀元)，小組嗰啲都拿到預期成績。有搞坊間嘅mock（幾百人）。上年，前年都有post過DSE Phy MC ANS。另外，都係9間中學教過奧林匹克，都有啲人識我。唔收生，讀書都超忙。<br />\n<br />\n如果有past paper，唔識做。<br />\n最好可以唔明啲咩，咁樣我先容易教到你明，否則，我就要估估下。<br />\n<br />\n如無意外，我每隔一兩日就post DSE物理嘅技巧/注意事項/LQ答題。<br />\n<br />\n今晚post部份heat嘅LQ答題字眼<br />\n<br />\n附圖:<br />\n2018 DSE Phy 成績<br />\nPaper 2玩野，所以考得比較差<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be312bc5bc9e05057cc98bd7e002afa4a1e4e55d","tid":1000362,"uid":110858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:54:59.000Z","msg":"兩個elective點溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd783f2f78ef6fe9d67d2acb92daada72d6e0a2","tid":1000362,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:06:49.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"e8fe5ed8d5cb39ece9b775bbf92100a0e239fe90","tid":1000362,"uid":171256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be312bc5bc9e05057cc98bd7e002afa4a1e4e55d","tid":1000362,"uid":110858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:54:59.000Z","msg":"兩個elective點溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:13:17.000Z","msg":"邊兩個？"},{"pid":"16132d7ef098342055ac154323b748545021a838","tid":1000362,"uid":110858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8fe5ed8d5cb39ece9b775bbf92100a0e239fe90","tid":1000362,"uid":171256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be312bc5bc9e05057cc98bd7e002afa4a1e4e55d","tid":1000362,"uid":110858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:54:59.000Z","msg":"兩個elective點溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:13:17.000Z","msg":"邊兩個？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:14:28.000Z","msg":"原子世界 能源"},{"pid":"e5e1317eb570f6147c9bb2b680878130db4f5a17","tid":1000362,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:17:09.000Z","msg":"咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d62a2613b9bc2a168038a3bedbea6472153bf49","tid":1000362,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"5想上5*/** 仲可以做d乜<br />\n<br />\nMarking係唔係要背?<br />\n<br />\nHkeaa syl 講到要定義既野，係咪要背埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce92691771b4a51c6e862d3d3fb748f851db5e9f","tid":1000362,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d8e988489e5d4716d71ad87750df47ee3b5c45","tid":1000362,"uid":160884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:59:12.000Z","msg":"仲有好多topic唔識，可以點追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3382bd0516005ff531b8b8875be38b59dce4ea8","tid":1000362,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X9dVEB6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX9dVEB6.jpg&h=b10a7b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2012 E3 marking 好似有少少問題?<br />\n我係試卷封面搵唔到任何指示，答案取乜近似值<br />\n3(a)佢用1000做都案都算(鉛筆係真確值)<br />\n但都冇理由照拎1000計下一題，咁d答案係愈來愈唔準?<br />\n<br />\n3(c)(i) 佢條式計出黎係14244.186個(事實上用999.13計係=14245.43965)<br />\n題目係問需要幾多個電池，姑且用佢marking既 14244.186個，好明顯要14245個先得 <br />\n<br />\n點會最後答案係14244架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e5ef75b49b51afe7ffcd197bdfe32244b1c858","tid":1000362,"uid":171256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3382bd0516005ff531b8b8875be38b59dce4ea8","tid":1000362,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X9dVEB6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX9dVEB6.jpg&h=b10a7b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2012 E3 marking 好似有少少問題?<br />\n我係試卷封面搵唔到任何指示，答案取乜近似值<br />\n3(a)佢用1000做都案都算(鉛筆係真確值)<br />\n但都冇理由照拎1000計下一題，咁d答案係愈來愈唔準?<br />\n<br />\n3(c)(i) 佢條式計出黎係14244.186個(事實上用999.13計係=14245.43965)<br />\n題目係問需要幾多個電池，姑且用佢marking既 14244.186個，好明顯要14245個先得 <br />\n<br />\n點會最後答案係14244架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:24:30.000Z","msg":"你呢份係建議答案，並非改卷嗰份marking scheme<br />\n一般答案取3s.f.<br />\n建議你拿多兩個位，尤其係要用落去計下一部份<br />\n<br />\n改卷嗰陣，會接受一個range嘅答案，所以14244或者14245都得"},{"pid":"d3c2fab0625cc95a349527c43c6ac0667d4f2f18","tid":1000362,"uid":171256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16132d7ef098342055ac154323b748545021a838","tid":1000362,"uid":110858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8fe5ed8d5cb39ece9b775bbf92100a0e239fe90","tid":1000362,"uid":171256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be312bc5bc9e05057cc98bd7e002afa4a1e4e55d","tid":1000362,"uid":110858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:54:59.000Z","msg":"兩個elective點溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:13:17.000Z","msg":"邊兩個？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:14:28.000Z","msg":"原子世界 能源"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:33:06.000Z","msg":"當然有嘅past paper/sample paper/practice paper都要做晒。<br />\n<br />\n原子世界，光電效應同玻爾模型都有AL past paper做晒佢，記晒marking。納米嗰部份臨考前要溫一次書嘅例子，同STM TEM結構同運作原理。<br />\n<br />\n遲下，我要幫幾個中六溫呢課，我整完中文版嘅brief note再放上黎<br />\n<br />\n能源<br />\n呢課，我都覺得難溫，你有無咩topic特別唔識/唔明？"},{"pid":"3a7cae12db2dd7cf51d994034348a996d9441c1e","tid":1000362,"uid":171256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d62a2613b9bc2a168038a3bedbea6472153bf49","tid":1000362,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"5想上5*/** 仲可以做d乜<br />\n<br />\nMarking係唔係要背?<br />\n<br />\nHkeaa syl 講到要定義既野，係咪要背埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:38:00.000Z","msg":"我唔知你大概幾多分，5上5*都要10分，<br />\n上5**要16-18分(有啲難度)<br />\n<br />\n你應該做晒一次past paper? Mark down自己做錯，理解自己做錯啲咩。<br />\n<br />\n或者你講下自己通常錯啲咩？咁先可以對症下藥"},{"pid":"a062401efd5930d626b7131254ff9d588ee78e3d","tid":1000362,"uid":34277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T15:21:45.000Z","msg":"仲2018?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77343990693e885b486f4c1c7dc08757290513c5","tid":1000362,"uid":19431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"請問巴打實驗題有咩重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明成題都識，但永遠比日校老師扣咁一兩分，再問佢就會話出面都係一定唔比滿分"},{"pid":"d3a95d6b31b37738aefbab5dcfb1b808e7490f32","tid":1000362,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:43:57.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3f624fe254fd83bbb4417c63b2d2d7af03172d","tid":1000362,"uid":171256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77343990693e885b486f4c1c7dc08757290513c5","tid":1000362,"uid":19431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"請問巴打實驗題有咩重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明成題都識，但永遠比日校老師扣咁一兩分，再問佢就會話出面都係一定唔比滿分"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:50:47.000Z","msg":"介唔介意post你之前做過嘅實驗題？<br />\n<br />\n實驗題都會有少少基本套路，但要拿足分，咁真係要多做實驗，知道實驗儀器點用，同個次序<br />\n好難拿足分<br />\n<br />\n我之前crop左所有CE DSE Past Paper Experiment 題目"},{"pid":"ebb4191ba8736873d53c7d6430c86bec2c1e426b","tid":1000362,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a7cae12db2dd7cf51d994034348a996d9441c1e","tid":1000362,"uid":171256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d62a2613b9bc2a168038a3bedbea6472153bf49","tid":1000362,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"5想上5*/** 仲可以做d乜<br />\n<br />\nMarking係唔係要背?<br />\n<br />\nHkeaa syl 講到要定義既野，係咪要背埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:38:00.000Z","msg":"我唔知你大概幾多分，5上5*都要10分，<br />\n上5**要16-18分(有啲難度)<br />\n<br />\n你應該做晒一次past paper? Mark down自己做錯，理解自己做錯啲咩。<br />\n<br />\n或者你講下自己通常錯啲咩？咁先可以對症下藥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:13:17.000Z","msg":"感謝巴打解答<br />\n我計數多數都岩既，係要落筆解釋就失分<br />\n<br />\nMc就做左過20年，LQ暫時只做左約7,8年<br />\n我諗住做多d LQ再睇下點<br />\n<br />\n會考mc好似易好多咁?我同樣時間已經可以做完45條會考mc仲，仲淨十多分鐘，但做33條既dse都只係僅僅夠時間。但dse計埋sp pp都係得9年,想操多d dse程度既mc<br />\n<br />\n巴打點睇教圖本mock 作者姓鍾"},{"pid":"1d50ab9607f669d794d1c04dc51c3508b1521bfd","tid":1000362,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:18:19.000Z","msg":"仲有，其實AL topic(例如，氣體分子運動論)dse 係唔係唔會考太深，<br />\n只考到&quot;sub 數&quot;既level<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  至少我未見過dse問得好深入<br />\n坊間有d練習難到，好似做黎都哂氣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef59edd3dd58ab2f6487e899952503539a4f1b3","tid":1000362,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:20:14.000Z","msg":"請問oup同pearson呢兩本textbook邊本好D?<br />\n還是兩本都咁廢?"},{"pid":"91daac874ea6350c28d514025a00a2d91d533a43","tid":1000362,"uid":171256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebb4191ba8736873d53c7d6430c86bec2c1e426b","tid":1000362,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a7cae12db2dd7cf51d994034348a996d9441c1e","tid":1000362,"uid":171256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d62a2613b9bc2a168038a3bedbea6472153bf49","tid":1000362,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"5想上5*/** 仲可以做d乜<br />\n<br />\nMarking係唔係要背?<br />\n<br />\nHkeaa syl 講到要定義既野，係咪要背埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:38:00.000Z","msg":"我唔知你大概幾多分，5上5*都要10分，<br />\n上5**要16-18分(有啲難度)<br />\n<br />\n你應該做晒一次past paper? Mark down自己做錯，理解自己做錯啲咩。<br />\n<br />\n或者你講下自己通常錯啲咩？咁先可以對症下藥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:13:17.000Z","msg":"感謝巴打解答<br />\n我計數多數都岩既，係要落筆解釋就失分<br />\n